  <brief_title>Post-operative CRP Trend After Ileocolic Resection in Crohn's Disease Patients.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Post-operative CRP Trend May Lead to Early Diagnosis of Anastomotic Leak After Ileocolic Resection in Crohn's Disease Patients.</official_title>
