  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Our aim is to analyze C-Reactive Protein trends during the post-operative course in Crohn's&#xD;
      Disease patients having undergone ileocolic resection and primary anastomosis, for the&#xD;
      purpose of anastomotic leak early diagnosis.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
